title: Harper Beckham Rides a Pony See the Adorable Pic
text:
Harper Beckham Rides a Pony: See the Adorable Pic! 
E online Saturday 24th October, 2015 
, 4.The 41-year-old sometimes-Spice Girl took her daughter Harper for a pony ride out on a ranch this week in California and, of course, the result was adorable. The little girl rode saddle back and as too cute in her riding pants, polo shirt and a long fancy braid, taking after her mom in true posh style.
